      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/kenya-to-tighten-control-of-social-media-amid-anti-ruto-backlash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚计划加强对社交媒体的监管，以应对网络暴力，而该国总统威廉·鲁托 (William Ruto) 也遭到了越来越多的批评。]]></description>
