      <title>私募股权公司利用南非莱利银行寻找肯尼亚糖果制造商股权的买家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/pe-firms-tap-nedbank-to-find-buyer-for-kenya-candy-maker-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，两家私募股权公司已聘请南非莱利银行集团有限公司 (Nedbank Group Ltd.) 出售其在东非最大糖果制造商的股份，价值超过 1 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/pe-firms-tap-nedbank-to-find-buyer-for-kenya-candy-maker-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 08:14:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
